# pip uninstall

> Uninstall Python packages
> More information: https://pip.pypa.io

- Uninstall a package:

`pip uninstall {string value: package_name}`

- Uninstall packages listed in a specific file:

`pip uninstall --requirement {string value: path/to/requirements.txt}`

- Uninstall package without asking for confirmation:

`pip uninstall --yes {string value: package_name}`
